    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You are wielding an Ethereal Chain in your hand</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">            </span>Your ethereal chain elongates as you strike at the target area, creating a small eruption of chains to strike out of the earth and entangle your enemies.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">            </span>Upon casting this spell, you deal 2d6 slashing damage to each creature in the area. Each creature must make a Reflex saving throw. At the end of this spell, your Ethereal Chain shatters.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Critical Success</strong> the creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Success </strong>the creature takes half damage and suffers a 10-foot circumstance penalty to its speeds for 1 round.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Failure</strong> the creature takes full damage and suffers a -10-foot circumstance penalty to its Speeds for 1 round.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Critical </strong>Failure the creature takes double damage and is immobilized for 1 round. Creatures can attempt to Escape at your spell DC to remove these effects.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Heightened(+2): </strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">The area of this spell increases by 5 feet, and the damage increases by 2d6.</span></p>"
    },
